{"tid":984744,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"藍領hea既時間已經超過好多文員","createTime":"2019-01-17T04:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:34:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"63dc3aa1284389379f2699b393f7208540726113","tid":984744,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"我有朋友個仔， 大學fg係大公司做文員仔（人工11k）， 忙到pk， 而且俾老細發現係返工時間玩手機， 即收warning letter....<br />\n<br />\n反而自手機進化後， 藍領hea既時間都開始超過好多基層文員。好似侍應， 售貨員， 保安咁， 搏殺兩小時左右， 就有十幾分鐘休息時間， 可以用果d時間去玩手機。<br />\n反而做私營機構文員仔， 好多時候要chur足四小時或以上， 無得間中玩手機。（當然做政府會hea好多）<br />\n<br />\n始終， 文員仔如果無專業資格， 係私營機構既人工同前途都有限， 比好多藍領更不如。（朋友個仔始終想做文職， 我勸佢去讀會計專業資格。）"},{"pid":"480d4eb60d3804e81f627b23df2581307cf04ef5","tid":984744,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"藍領有3點3<br />\n白領無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd8d0d03c838b6f411bd842a188e60d64701279","tid":984744,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480d4eb60d3804e81f627b23df2581307cf04ef5","tid":984744,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"藍領有3點3<br />\n白領無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"要自費"},{"pid":"42e3e9231a816e9c5c717f257bb34d2d7a3aa4fe","tid":984744,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"咁點 你咪去做"},{"pid":"329323afd491484584d94863e15e7ed69064a010","tid":984744,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"我相反咼...<br />\n好多時候要玩足四小時或以上"},{"pid":"8f3e7d52d99baa33251ae5410adc94f5d651cbff","tid":984744,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"公營文員表示我今朝睇咗兩套戲 依家食完飯返去午睡"},{"pid":"d36c1c4d1142645e01586ad3962276fe2e4098d6","tid":984744,"uid":196924,"